  defn
  G |- mu  ::  ::storetype::'st_'
  {{ com store [[mu]] is well typed against context [[G]] }} 
  by

    -------------- :: empty
    empty |- empty


    G |> vi : Ti <| G
    Ti <: Ui
    ------------------------------------------------ :: vars
    </ xi : Ui // i /> |- </ xi |-> vi // i />


