  defn
  O @ SSet sim O' @ SSet' ::  ::simulation::'sim_'
  {{ com [[O]]@[[SSet]] is a simulation of [[O']]@[[SSet']]}} by

  defn
  T <: T'  ::  ::subtype::'sub_'
  {{ com [[T]] is a subtype of [[T']] }}
  by

    ------- :: refl
    T <: T


    T <: U
    U <: V
    ------- :: trans
    T <: V

    Ui <: Ti
    Ti' <: Ui'
    T <: U
    --------------------------------------------------------------- :: fn
    ( </ Ti >> Ti' // i /> ) -> T <: ( </ Ui >> Ui' // i /> ) -> U'


    O @ SSet sim O' @ SSet'
